Privacy Policy
Last Updated: March 25, 2024

1. Information We Collect
I Vocab collects the following types of information:
• Vocabulary words and their definitions that you add
• Your learning progress and quiz results
• App usage statistics to improve user experience

2. How We Use Your Information
We use the collected information to:
• Provide and improve our vocabulary learning services
• Personalize your learning experience
• Send you notifications for learning reminders
• Analyze app usage to enhance functionality

3. Data Storage
Your vocabulary data is stored locally on your device. We do not store your personal information on external servers unless you explicitly choose to use our backup feature.

4. Data Security
We implement appropriate security measures to protect your data. However, no method of transmission over the internet is 100% secure.

5. Third-Party Services
I Vocab does not share your data with third-party services except for essential app functionality (e.g., app store analytics).

6. Your Rights
You have the right to:
• Access your personal data
• Delete your data from the app
• Opt-out of notifications

7. Contact Us
If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us through Discord. 
